<h3>Graphing tool</h3>
	<p>
		<h4 id="conditional"><i class="flare-func"></i>conditional</h4>
		<label>Syntax:</label> <code>conditional(...args)</code>
		<label>Arguments:</label>
		<ul>
			<li><code>...args</code> - value + condition pairs</li>
		</ul>
		<label>Return value:</label> a function that takes one argument.
		<label>Brief:</label><p>
		Returns a function that iterates through all of the
		<code>args</code> and takes the first value of which the condition
		was satisfied with the given value.
		</p>
		<label>Example:</label>
		<p><pre>
conditional(
	[ x =&gt; - x - 7, x => x &lt; -5 ],
	[ x =&gt; -2 * x ** 2 - 12 * x - 12, _ =&gt; true ]
);</pre>
		Returns <code>-x - 7</code> if <code>x is &lt; -5</code> and
		<code>-2 * x ** 2 - 12 * x - 12</code> otherwise.</p>
	</p>
    

